&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We’re seeking a highly collaborative, detail-oriented Deal Desk Manager Contractor to support Armada’s global Deal Desk and GTM teams. This role sits within the Revenue Operations organization and partners with Sales, Legal, and Finance to ensure deals move quickly, accurately, and compliantly from quote to close.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
