&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This is a senior commercial role that sits at the intersection of AI infrastructure, compute demand, and business development. You will build the demand side of Armada&#39;s AI factory business&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;originating, qualifying, and converting offtake demand for GPU capacity across our AI factory and Leviathan deployments.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:60,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:80}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
