&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;If&amp;nbsp;you&#39;re&amp;nbsp;deeply networked in the AI compute ecosystem, have&amp;nbsp;a track record&amp;nbsp;of commercializing GPU infrastructure or cloud capacity, and want to help build something important at the infrastructure layer of AI&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;this role is for you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:60,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:80}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
